Program: The Documentary
Title: Gadgets and Green Ink
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00cdn4n
Last Broadcast Date: Sat 18 Dec 2010
An unprecedented look inside MI6 - Britain's Secret Intelligence Service, which marked its centenary in 2009. For this three-part series, BBC security correspondent Gordon Corera talks to senior intelligence officers, agents and diplomats as well as their former arch enemies about the shadowy world of espionage. Show less